  <div class="container">
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Welcome to the CursedMC Staff Team</h2>
      <p>This guide will help you understand your responsibilities and how to be an effective staff member. As a staff
        member, you are the face of CursedMC both on and off the server.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>General Staff Rules</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You may not use your permissions/status to gain an advantage over players & other staff</li>
        <li>You are not allowed to leak/reveal any sensitive information regarding the staff team</li>
        <li>Remain professional at all times - you can have fun in the chat but remain sensitive</li>
        <li>You must use staff chat if speaking to fellow colleagues regarding staff information</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>How to Issue a Punishment</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Collect Evidence - Screenshots, core protect logs, photo evidence, or video recordings</li>
        <li>View user's history using /history [player]</li>
        <li>Check punishment guidelines</li>
        <li>Issue the punishment with the offense attached</li>
        <li>Submit evidence and fill out the required formats</li>
      </ol>

      <h3>In-Game Punishment Format</h3>
      <div class="example">
        <p>IGN: _nodms</p>
        <p>Punishment: Ban</p>
        <p>Length of punishment: 7d</p>
        <p>Reason: Cheating</p>
        <p>Offense: 1</p>
        <p>Evidence: (Video required for cheating)</p>
      </div>

      <h3>Discord Punishment Format</h3>
      <div class="example">
